  "title": "HR Executive (Recruitment/Manufacturing, East Region)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage full recruitment lifecycle from sourcing to onboarding.</li>\n  <li>Implement hiring strategies via job portals, agencies, and events.</li>\n  <li>Set recruitment targets and timelines to meet business needs.</li>\n  <li>Screen, interview, and recommend candidates to hiring managers.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with staffing agencies and coordinate interview processes.</li>\n  <li>Prepare recruitment reports and ensure regulatory compliance.</li>\n  <li>Conduct exit interviews and provide retention feedback.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 2 years of full-cycle recruitment experience, preferably in semiconductor or manufacturing.</li>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in HR, Business, Engineering, or related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Experienced in handling high-volume hiring.</li>\n  <li>Strong Excel skills (VLOOKUP, Pivot), Outlook, and database systems; SAP is an added advantage.</li>\n  <li>Experience in non-executive recruitment is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p>\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p>\n<p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
